{"tid":2074111,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇聯 定 依家既共黨 講大話 厲害D?","createTime":"2020-06-22T00:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T00:54:20.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d499fd3689954afeefc95bac3358e29aa8a55bd9","tid":2074111,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:51:06.000Z","msg":"厲害了 我的謊言國 <br />\n蘇聯前總理雷日科夫說：我們監守自盜，行賄受賄，無論在報紙、新聞還是講台上，都謊話連篇，一面沉溺於自己的謊言，一面彼此佩戴獎章。所有人都這麼幹，從上到下，從下到上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ea_0tf1UcAEEiZL?format=png&amp;name=360x360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEa_0tf1UcAEEiZL%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3D360x360&h=4a43292c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共不但是編造謊言的行家，而且也是傳播謊言的高手。就其統治大陸後而言，中共的謊言傳播首先是一種帶有明顯強制性的傳播。也就是說，作為受眾的廣大民眾，在面對這種傳播時是沒有選擇餘地的，不管你願意也吧不願意也吧，也不管你樂於接受還是想要逃避，你都必須接受這種傳播&mdash;&mdash;至於你內心是否真地接受那則是另一回事。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fdd5f70ba1a9fc3c355a431026823c93fda9c5","tid":2074111,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/02/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%88%87%E7%88%BE%E8%AB%BE%E8%B2%9D%E7%88%BEChernobyl-20200208214844_e4e9_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2588%2587%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25B2%259D%25E7%2588%25BEChernobyl-20200208214844_e4e9_large.jpg&h=694b2d8c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}